* TclArgv -- C-side argument parsing for Tcl commands
* in the flavour of TkArgv.
*************************************
This concept has been accepted for inclusion into Tcl 8.6.
See TIP#265 http://www.tcl.tk/cgi-bin/tct/tip/view/265

The variant there is a little different. The code here is what
I am using until Tcl 8.6 comes out.
